    "description": "<strong>我们的游戏现已发布简体中文版本，</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/897487379b072e9d1e3fe9a97fac4c01.avif?t=1725400648\" width=800 height=113 /></span><br><br>一堆稿件摞在您的办公桌上，左右各有一个一张 - 绿色表示通过，红色表示退回。扬声器播放着公司的音乐，您的报导团队正在幕后努力撰写文稿。现在，您该做决定了。在您的挚爱之人对不断延长的候诊时间忧心忡忡的时候，您是否会对医疗保健事业的国有化表示支持？在您的老板一再强调，新推出的合成酒精饮料制造商是公司的重要投资方时，您是否会对这种饮料大加抨击？随着邻国之间的紧张局势加剧，您会对现任政府表示支持吗？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/0064e75070e7397a77525c7644a6702c.poster.avif?t=1725400648\" width=618 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/0064e75070e7397a77525c7644a6702c.webm?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/0064e75070e7397a77525c7644a6702c.mp4?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>下班后，您会出现在诺维斯坦的大街上。大街的样貌取决于您发布的新闻 - 也许您会看到更多的涂鸦、愤怒的流浪汉甚至是一场暴乱？也许您会让这个国家变成和平的乌托邦，遍布摄像机和无人机，密切注视着您迈出的每一步？对于即将发生的悲剧事件，您的频道将如何处理？您是否愿意与讲真话的秘密团体会面，或是停下脚步，观看总理的讲话？<br> <br><br>在回家的路上，你遇到了三个主要角色：埃维，移民，你的同事，担心自己的监控状况和愈来愈强的排外情绪；你的兄弟贾斯汀，一个有抱负的喜剧演员，与冒名顶替综合症和社交焦虑症苦战；最后这位是鲁迪，一位单身父亲，为了自己的小女儿努力拼搏，在隔壁开张了超级市场之后，希望自己的小店能够逃过破产命运。每天，您都能一瞥他们的生活，了解媒体对他们心中信仰的影响。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/92036e3ab7c659532798b37e7acce82c.avif?t=1725400648\" width=600 height=332 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/1fc93c8f40e97541751553bf40adc23b.poster.avif?t=1725400648\" width=300 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/1fc93c8f40e97541751553bf40adc23b.webm?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/1fc93c8f40e97541751553bf40adc23b.mp4?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/6f900b326cc7aa7fdbaa170bdab6b44d.poster.avif?t=1725400648\" width=300 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/6f900b326cc7aa7fdbaa170bdab6b44d.webm?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/6f900b326cc7aa7fdbaa170bdab6b44d.mp4?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但每个头条主编都应该在家疏解工作带来的紧张。在窗外城市燃烧熊熊火焰之时，躺在用自己辛苦赚来钱币购买的舒适沙发上听收音机。也许您会选择在狗狗的点心上一掷千金？也许您会购买一台无人机？也许喊兄弟过来共进晚餐？又或者，在自己公寓里缓慢堆积起大堆现金的时候，关上大门，将每分每厘都收藏妥当？<br><br><br>一夜美梦之后，又要再次面对老板、新的新闻稿、越来越重的责任感以及... 权力。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/7597ae5dded02f2e33efa062756fcb51.poster.avif?t=1725400648\" width=624 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/7597ae5dded02f2e33efa062756fcb51.webm?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/7597ae5dded02f2e33efa062756fcb51.mp4?t=1725400648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/918820/extras/66522a61fd6b27fc49a0cf30aba0731a.avif?t=1725400648\" width=800 height=106 /></span><br><i>* 一定要看两次……#假新闻 #悲伤</i>",
